
1) The installation instruction comes from: http://www.roman10.net/how-to-build-ffmpeg-with-ndk-r9/

2) export NDK environment variable. e.g. export NDK=/opt/adt-bundle-linux-x86_64/ndk

3) Linux: ./build_android.sh
   Mac: ./build_android_for_mac.sh

NOTICE

 - Non system dependencies (e.g. libx264, libvpx) are disabled by default.
